{"id":"jezreel-blood-of","term":"Jezreel, Blood of","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The murder perpetrated here by Ahab and Jehu (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Hosea 1:4\">Hos. 1:4</a>; comp. <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 18:4\">1 Kings 18:4</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Kings 9:6\">2 Kings 9:6-10</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Hosea 1:4","1 Kings 18:4","2 Kings 9:6"]}